# Edge Transfer Debugging Rules

## 🔍 Current Issue Context
Agent Copy system works perfectly (✅) but workflow.edges remains 0 despite node.connections being populated.

## 📋 Debugging Priority Order

### 1. RealTimeWorkflowBuilder Logger Issue
**Problem**: `🔗 [NODE-CONNECTIONS]` logs not appearing despite extraction logic existing
**Check**: RealTimeWorkflowBuilder uses SilentLogger instead of ConsoleLogger

```typescript
// Current issue pattern in [real-time-workflow-builder.ts](mdc:packages/agents/src/services/real-time-workflow-builder.ts)
const workflowBuilder = new RealTimeWorkflowBuilder(workflowSubscriber); // No logger passed
```

**Required Fix**: Pass DefaultConsoleLogger to RealTimeWorkflowBuilder constructor

### 2. Connection Extraction Timing
**Problem**: establishConnections() may not be called for Agent Copy nodes
**Check**: Verify node.connections exist when establishConnections() is called

```typescript
// Debug pattern needed in establishConnections()
console.log(`🔧 [DEBUG] Node ${node.id} has ${node.connections?.length || 0} connections`);
```

### 3. Workflow Structure Integrity
**Problem**: currentWorkflow.connections vs final workflow.edges mismatch
**Check**: Verify connections persist through workflow building pipeline

## 🎯 Specific Debugging Steps

### Step 1: Logger Fix
```typescript
// In examples/26-playground-edge-verification.ts
const workflowBuilder = new RealTimeWorkflowBuilder(workflowSubscriber, DefaultConsoleLogger);
```

### Step 2: Connection Validation
```typescript
// Add to establishConnections() in real-time-workflow-builder.ts
if (node.connections && node.connections.length > 0) {
  this.logger.debug(`🔧 [DEBUG] Processing ${node.connections.length} connections for ${node.id}`);
  // ... existing extraction logic
}
```

### Step 3: Workflow Pipeline Verification
```typescript
// Add to getCurrentWorkflow() in real-time-workflow-builder.ts
this.logger.debug(`📊 [PIPELINE] Final workflow: ${this.currentWorkflow.nodes.length} nodes, ${this.currentWorkflow.connections.length} edges`);
```

## 🚨 Critical Success Criteria

1. **NODE-CONNECTIONS logs appear**: Confirms extraction logic executes
2. **workflow.connections > 0**: Confirms connections are added to workflow
3. **workflow.edges > 0**: Confirms final pipeline success
4. **Cached execution**: Use cached results for rapid debugging iteration

